    {
      "primitive": {
        "name": "hydra.lib.maps.alter",
        "metadata": {
          "description": "Alter a value at a key using a function which sees the optional current value.",
          "comments": [
            "alter(f, k, m) applies f to Just(v) when m contains key k with value v, or to Nothing when k is absent. If f returns Just(v'), the binding (k, v') is set in the result; if f returns Nothing, k is removed from the result.",
            "A single primitive that subsumes insert, delete, and adjust.",
            "Requires an 'ordering' constraint on the key type.",
            "Total. Corresponds to Haskell's Data.Map.alter :: Ord k => (Maybe v -> Maybe v) -> k -> Map k v -> Map k v."],
          "seeAlso": []},
        "signature": {
          "typeParameters": [{"name": "v", "constraints": []}, {"name": "k", "constraints": [{"simple": "ordering"}]}],
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "f",
              "description": "the update function, applied to the optional current value at the key",
              "type": {"function": {"domain": {"optional": {"variable": "v"}}, "codomain": {"optional": {"variable": "v"}}}},
              "isLazy": false},
            {"name": "k", "description": "the key whose binding to alter", "type": {"variable": "k"}, "isLazy": false},
            {
              "name": "m",
              "description": "the map to update",
              "type": {"map": {"keys": {"variable": "k"}, "values": {"variable": "v"}}},
              "isLazy": false}],
          "result": {"type": {"map": {"keys": {"variable": "k"}, "values": {"variable": "v"}}}}},
        "isPure": true,
        "isTotal": true,
        "defaultImplementation": {
          "lambda": {
            "parameter": "f",
            "body": {
              "lambda": {
                "parameter": "k",
                "body": {
                  "lambda": {
                    "parameter": "m",
                    "body": {
                      "application": {
                        "function": {
                          "application": {
                            "function": {
                              "application": {
                                "function": {"variable": "hydra.lib.optionals.cases"},
                                "argument": {
                                  "application": {
                                    "function": {"variable": "f"},
                                    "argument": {
                                      "application": {
                                        "function": {"application": {"function": {"variable": "hydra.lib.maps.lookup"}, "argument": {"variable": "k"}}},
                                        "argument": {"variable": "m"}}}}}}},
                            "argument": {
                              "application": {
                                "function": {"application": {"function": {"variable": "hydra.lib.maps.delete"}, "argument": {"variable": "k"}}},
                                "argument": {"variable": "m"}}}}},
                        "argument": {
                          "lambda": {
                            "parameter": "vNew",
                            "body": {
                              "application": {
                                "function": {
                                  "application": {
                                    "function": {"application": {"function": {"variable": "hydra.lib.maps.insert"}, "argument": {"variable": "k"}}},
                                    "argument": {"variable": "vNew"}}},
                                "argument": {"variable": "m"}}}}}}}}}}}}}}},
    {
      "primitive": {
        "name": "hydra.lib.maps.bimap",
        "metadata": {
          "description": "Map functions over both the keys and values of a map.",
          "comments": [
            "bimap(fk, fv, m) returns a new map with key fk(k) and value fv(v) for each binding (k, v) in m.",
            "Key collisions after applying fk are resolved by keeping the last binding encountered (host may differ on collision policy if fk is not injective).",
            "Requires 'ordering' constraints on both the input and output key types.",
            "Total. Corresponds to a key-and-value lift of Haskell's Data.Map.fromList . map (\\(k,v) -> (fk k, fv v)) . toList."],
          "seeAlso": []},
        "signature": {
          "typeParameters": [
            {"name": "k1", "constraints": [{"simple": "ordering"}]},
            {"name": "k2", "constraints": [{"simple": "ordering"}]},
            {"name": "v1", "constraints": []},
            {"name": "v2", "constraints": []}],
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "fk",
              "description": "the function to apply to each key",
              "type": {"function": {"domain": {"variable": "k1"}, "codomain": {"variable": "k2"}}},
              "isLazy": false},
            {
              "name": "fv",
              "description": "the function to apply to each value",
              "type": {"function": {"domain": {"variable": "v1"}, "codomain": {"variable": "v2"}}},
              "isLazy": false},
            {
              "name": "m",
              "description": "the map to transform",
              "type": {"map": {"keys": {"variable": "k1"}, "values": {"variable": "v1"}}},
              "isLazy": false}],
          "result": {"type": {"map": {"keys": {"variable": "k2"}, "values": {"variable": "v2"}}}}},
        "isPure": true,
        "isTotal": true,
        "defaultImplementation": {
          "lambda": {
            "parameter": "fk",
            "body": {
              "lambda": {
                "parameter": "fv",
                "body": {
                  "lambda": {
                    "parameter": "m",
                    "body": {
                      "application": {
                        "function": {"variable": "hydra.lib.maps.fromList"},
                        "argument": {
                          "application": {
                            "function": {
                              "application": {
                                "function": {"variable": "hydra.lib.lists.map"},
                                "argument": {
                                  "lambda": {
                                    "parameter": "p",
                                    "body": {
                                      "pair": {
                                        "first": {
                                          "application": {
                                            "function": {"variable": "fk"},
                                            "argument": {"application": {"function": {"variable": "hydra.lib.pairs.first"}, "argument": {"variable": "p"}}}}},
                                        "second": {
                                          "application": {
                                            "function": {"variable": "fv"},
                                            "argument": {"application": {"function": {"variable": "hydra.lib.pairs.second"}, "argument": {"variable": "p"}}}}}}}}}}},
                            "argument": {"application": {"function": {"variable": "hydra.lib.maps.toList"}, "argument": {"variable": "m"}}}}}}}}}}}}}}},
